The paper discusses model-based strategies for control in continuous state domains, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses planning and simulation, which are common topics in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper introduces a semi-parametric model learning approach, which is a common topic in deep learning (cs.DL).
